{"tid":433982,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人生活過得好充實，但都仲係好空虛咁","createTime":"2017-10-13T00:43:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T16:17:04.000Z","uid":24642,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6692cd709a5d680a9da8ce809ced4a9a25cb07","tid":433982,"uid":24642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:43:20.000Z","msg":"早一排因為情緒問題，成日亂諗嘢，搞到好唔健康<br />\n唔想自己人生繼續差落去<br />\n於是的起心肝去改變現狀<br />\n<br />\n閒餘時間開始睇書、做運動、約朋友食好西<br />\n近排返份工，都尚算有滿足感，同事相處都幾好<br />\n望落好似好充實<br />\n<br />\n明明已經努力去塑造自己想要嘅人生<br />\n點解都仲係開心唔起<br />\n瞓得唔好，發埋啲怪夢，晚晚半夜扎醒<br />\n我係咪好賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5721db4c37509b6d7b6cb248bda04894a8865acc","tid":433982,"uid":8598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T00:46:17.000Z","msg":"解鈴還須繫鈴人"},{"pid":"183cae6a7a6477a495a2039a82323ef647972bc8","tid":433982,"uid":46752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:02:58.000Z","msg":"庸人自擾"},{"pid":"4ed209d319357aa5d196f0c49c51cbce0e307438","tid":433982,"uid":24642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:45:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>庸人自擾</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該係"},{"pid":"5bf6e9df7c567d9fb95f66939546632bc8f56e1a","tid":433982,"uid":113775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"有<br />\n明明日日都要返工搵錢！又要溫習讀書<br />\n忙都休息時間都冇<br />\n但仲係好空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可以因為太辛苦，所以好想搵到一個心靈交流到嘅另一伴分擔下壓力"},{"pid":"1044e096c1ce9a14cb40bddce73406fbad875997","tid":433982,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:52:00.000Z","msg":"空虛"},{"pid":"b70e40541b4241abbf5a02fd2b7ecd5e3f1d8bae","tid":433982,"uid":35106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:55:32.000Z","msg":"長期空虛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji